<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-88-0880 </DOCNO><TEXT>On September 28, 1986, the Senate passed the compromise version of theTax Reform Act of 1986. The Tax Reform Act makes major changes in thetreatment of cogeneration and alternative energy projects, and many ofthe significant tax advantages currently enjoyed by the cogenerationand alternative energy industries are lost under the Act. This articlesummarizes the key provisions of the Tax Reform Act for cogenerationand alternative energy projects.</TEXT></DOC>